episodes.title: The Cult Leader Who Faked a God… With a Puppet
episodes.description:
He claimed to have discovered a forgotten god… and thousands believed him. But the truth? It was something else entirely. Join me as we dive into one of history’s most bizarre cons — complete with oracles, miracles, and yes… a puppet.

Subscribe for more true stories ➔ ☕✨

A dramatised story inspired by true events.
